{"tid":732374,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚基沙文入波唔慶祝睇到好感動","createTime":"2018-07-07T00:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T14:48:29.000Z","uid":24220,"like":447,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"adae2b7b926d1a2de2dfa0451e36c2e0e5f9c249","tid":732374,"uid":24220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T00:57:04.000Z","msg":"兩年前輸左歐國決賽，好明白去到呢d大賽淘汰階段輸波既心情<br />\n琴晚個球，可以話係射得夠飄，或者入得夠-6，但個責任9成都係係烏龜個龍度<br />\n大賽犯呢d錯誤真係會影響好大，有機會一沉不起（eg 費托對獌球空龍）<br />\n基沙文選擇唔慶祝，真心好欣賞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71427a155329ce25fa142e343c52b10a3ca666b2","tid":732374,"uid":82304,"like":248,"dislike":3,"score":245,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:09:23.000Z","msg":"佢當自己係半個烏拉圭人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc63760343b5e78586db594a8be1deecdaa47af","tid":732374,"uid":54359,"like":126,"dislike":2,"score":124,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:11:10.000Z","msg":"佢同高甸合作左咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9475d8b3136bf6301c8d5b87cc5ecd270e9b642d","tid":732374,"uid":58811,"like":204,"dislike":7,"score":197,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:12:16.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更加顯到之前西班牙拉狗更賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ed4ae97a1a92d78afd38c1d04c457c13320f88","tid":732374,"uid":58811,"like":10,"dislike":17,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"71427a155329ce25fa142e343c52b10a3ca666b2","tid":732374,"uid":82304,"like":248,"dislike":3,"score":245,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:09:23.000Z","msg":"佢當自己係半個烏拉圭人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"其實佢咁講都幾on9"},{"pid":"134a43392cb53f918d7aca79e3a41472779febe0","tid":732374,"uid":82304,"like":174,"dislike":1,"score":173,"quote":{"pid":"8